  "excerpt": "<p>See if you\u2019re qualified for a tax exemption. What to do without form 1095-A</p>",
  "content": "<p>If you didn\u2019t have coverage during 2025, the fee no longer applies. This means you don\u2019t need an <a href=\"/health-coverage-exemptions/exemptions-from-the-fee\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"502e1f0b-ce3d-4282-bb3f-1f8a098849bd\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-bundle=\"article\" data-entity-id=\"37406\" data-internal-href target title=\"Exemptions from the requirement to have health insurance\">exemption</a> in order to avoid the penalty.</p><div class=\"box-content information-lightweight\"><p><strong>Some states charge a fee if you don't have health coverage&nbsp;</strong></p><p>If you live in a state that requires you to have health coverage and you don\u2019t have coverage (or an exemption), you\u2019ll be charged a fee when you file your 2025 state taxes. Check with your state or tax preparer.</p></div><p><strong>You will NOT get Form 1095-A</strong> unless you or someone in your household had Marketplace coverage for all or part of 2025.</p><p><a href=\"/tax-form-1095#find-1095-a\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"6382f2ee-1765-433e-8f35-d21232410087\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"36146\" data-entity-bundle=\"article\" title=\"How to use Form 1095-A\">Learn how to find your Form 1095-A.</a></p><h3>Tax forms and instructions:</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.irs.gov/pub/irs-pdf/f1040.pdf\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"6e53decb-cbd9-410d-b50d-c544e43f62aa\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"40496\" data-entity-bundle=\"link\" title=\"IRS Form 1040 - 2025\">Form 1040, U.S. Individual Income Tax Return</a> (PDF, 215 KB) and <a href=\"https://www.irs.gov/pub/irs-pdf/i1040gi.pdf\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"bb01966e-6b89-4a2e-82f7-176af7927fad\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"40501\" data-entity-bundle=\"link\" title=\"IRS Form 1040 Instructions - 2025\">Form 1040 instructions</a> (PDF, 4.2 MB).<br><a href=\"https://www.irs.gov/filing/individuals/how-to-file\">Find help preparing and filing your taxes.</a></p><p><a href=\"/how-can-i-protect-myself-from-tax-scams\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"90d7219e-fa4d-49d8-9a65-3adb840014ba\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"36086\" data-entity-bundle=\"article\" title=\"Protect yourself from tax scams\">Protect yourself from tax scams.</a></p><h2>More than one type of coverage?</h2><p>If you had no coverage for only part of 2025, or other household members had different coverage, select the other coverage:</p><ul><li><a href=\"/taxes/marketplace-plan-with-savings\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"9a183698-0dcb-4817-9e65-9f7fccf6bbb6\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"36171\" data-entity-bundle=\"article\" title=\"If you had a Marketplace plan with the premium tax credit\">Marketplace plan with the premium tax credit</a></li><li><a href=\"/taxes/marketplace-plan-without-savings\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"a0921806-0c09-4403-a273-eecd83603d95\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"36176\" data-entity-bundle=\"article\" title=\"If you had a Marketplace plan without the premium tax credit\">Marketplace plan without the premium tax credit</a></li><li><a href=\"/taxes/job-based-insurance\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"f00713df-ce1f-4edd-8afb-94ab4c8e54a5\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"36166\" data-entity-bundle=\"article\" title=\"If you had job-based health coverage\">Job-based health coverage</a></li><li><a href=\"/taxes/other-health-coverage\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"4865fa4c-88c1-431f-b482-0eab2d0a6457\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"36186\" data-entity-bundle=\"article\" title=\"If you had other health coverage\">Other health coverage</a></li></ul><div data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"21885ea5-8cc5-4b26-ab46-691347e9bcf3\" data-embed-button=\"brief\" data-entity-embed-display=\"view_mode:node.inline\" data-langcode=\"en\" data-entity-embed-display-settings=\"[]\" class=\"embedded-entity\">\n<article class=\"node node--type-brief node--view-mode-inline\">\n\n  \n    \n\n  \n  <div class=\"node__content\">\n    \n            <div class=\"clearfix text-formatted field field--name-field-content-body field--type-text-long field--label-hidden field__item\"><h2>Other tax years</h2><ul><li><a href=\"/taxes-2024/how-coverage-affects-taxes\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"b33efc77-6f55-4e10-b324-31969274517a\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"40431\" data-entity-bundle=\"article\" title=\"How health coverage affects your 2024 federal income tax return\">2024 taxes</a></li><li><a href=\"/taxes-2023/how-coverage-affects-taxes\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"4a81c2e1-4c04-48f1-a6e7-e3297ce41cec\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"40261\" data-entity-bundle=\"article\" title=\"How health coverage affects your 2023 federal income tax return\">2023 taxes</a></li><li><a href=\"/taxes-2022/how-coverage-affects-taxes\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"8d6d56f2-e511-49bd-9b10-d2418687d6f5\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"39826\" data-entity-bundle=\"article\" title=\"How health coverage affects your 2022 federal income tax return\">2022 taxes</a></li><li><a href=\"/taxes-2021/how-coverage-affects-taxes\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"0f722923-3f01-4ee5-a880-903622d6d43b\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"38236\" data-entity-bundle=\"article\" title=\"How health coverage affects your 2021 federal income tax return\">2021 taxes</a></li><li><a href=\"/taxes-2020/how-coverage-affects-taxes\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"1c1ea020-180c-4959-9f3c-4fb1a8fa7d51\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"36766\" data-entity-bundle=\"article\" title=\"How health coverage affects your 2020 federal income tax return\">2020 taxes</a></li><li><a href=\"/taxes-2019/how-coverage-affects-taxes\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"8d9b1ebd-930d-4552-a3b6-482a707d9894\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"36736\" data-entity-bundle=\"article\" title=\"How health coverage affects your 2019 federal income tax return\">2019 taxes</a></li><li><a href=\"/taxes-2018/how-coverage-affects-taxes\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"8b6e5121-9911-4ee8-8bb3-a6a5705475a5\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"36706\" data-entity-bundle=\"article\" title=\"How health coverage affects your 2018 federal income tax return\">2018 taxes</a></li></ul></div>\n      \n  </div>\n\n</article>\n</div>\n",
